    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> * ChessPartner</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://sjeng.org/deepsjeng.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/CPsshot2.png/300px-CPsshot2.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/6/65/CPsshot2.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:CPsshot2.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Deep_Sjeng\" title=\"Deep Sjeng\">Deep Sjeng</a> under <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ChessPartner</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>ChessPartner</b>,<br />\na  fully developed, commercial <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> market by <a href=\"/Lokasoft\" title=\"Lokasoft\">Lokasoft</a>, incorporating its native chess engine <a href=\"/LChess\" title=\"LChess\">LChess</a> and supporting any <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> or <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine via its internal adapter. ChessPartner evolved from the LChess GUI by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ger_Neef&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ger Neef (page does not exist)\">Ger Neef</a>, ported to Windows 3.0 in 1991 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Online_Client\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Online Client</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Databases\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Databases</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#GUI\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GUI</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Screenshots\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshots</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Online_Client\">Online Client</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Online Client\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>ChessPartner features as client for online play with various <a href=\"/Chess_Server\" title=\"Chess Server\">Chess Server</a> to challenge and play against other human players or engines. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Databases\">Databases</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Databases\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>ChessPartner has its own proprietary <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">database</a> format and also supports <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a>. Its <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> manager handels up to eight books in parallel and supports <a href=\"/Book_Learning\" title=\"Book Learning\">book learning</a>. Further, ChessPartner can query <a href=\"/Nalimov_Tablebases\" title=\"Nalimov Tablebases\">Nalimov endgame tablebases</a>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GUI\">GUI</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: GUI\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The ChessPartner GUI consists of a frame window, with caption-, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Status_bar\">status-</a>, and customizable <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Menu_bar\">menu-</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toolbar\">toolbar</a>, and a workspace with multiple views on the current game document, board window, optionally a <a href=\"/3D_Graphics_Board\" title=\"3D Graphics Board\">3D Board</a> with 3D-piece bitmaps, <a href=\"/Game_Notation\" title=\"Game Notation\">notation-</a>, <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">score-history-</a>, <a href=\"/Search_Statistics\" title=\"Search Statistics\">search-</a> and book statistics, chess clock-, and chess server console windows.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshots\">Screenshots</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshots\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/chesspartner.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Chesspartner.jpg\" src=\"/images/6/6f/Chesspartner.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"398\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>ChessPartner 6, 3D pieces <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Aquarium\" title=\"Aquarium\">Aquarium</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fritz#FritzGUI\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jose (page does not exist)\">jose</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shredder\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/ccff9c16b2022c6a\">ChessPartner 4.0 available</a>  by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, October 09, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=47677\">ChessPartner 4.1 released</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 31, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/aaf616dee7d5e8fe\">ChessPartner 4.2 available</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, October 11, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=89274\">ChessPartner 4.2 interface</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=118709\">ChessPartner Summer updates + Java chess</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 11, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=139886\">ChessPartner 5.0 available</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=192407\">ChessPartner 5.1 released</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=198832\">Pocket ChessPartner 1.0 released</a> by <a href=\"/Lex_Loep\" title=\"Lex Loep\">Lex Loep</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=316809\">Chesspartner and other GUIs</a> by <a href=\"/Russell_Reagan\" title=\"Russell Reagan\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 20, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=25912\">ChessPartner 6 released by end of January</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Marek_Soszynski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Marek Soszynski (page does not exist)\">Marek Soszynski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26401\">Opinions of ChessPartner 6.0</a> by <a href=\"/Ted_Summers\" title=\"Ted Summers\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2009 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37471\">Chess Partner GUI</a> by <a href=\"/Fernando_Villegas\" title=\"Fernando Villegas\">Fernando Villegas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2011</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/chesspartner.aspx\">ChessPartner - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesspartner.com/chesspartner-manual/\">ChessPartner 6.0: online manual</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/history.aspx\">History of ChessPartner - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/mobile_chesspartner.aspx\">Mobile ChessPartner - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/chesspartner-ios.aspx\">ChessPartner ios - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.geenvis.net/cplay.html\">Chesspartner stuff</a>  by <a href=\"/Fonzy_Bluemers\" title=\"Fonzy Bluemers\">Fonzy Bluemers</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPartner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sjeng.org/deepsjeng.html\">Sjeng - chess, audio and misc. software</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/history.aspx\">History of ChessPartner - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lokasoft.nl/chesspartner.aspx\">ChessPartner Screen shots | ChessPartner - Lokasoft - Home of ChessPartner</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301003102\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 89/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 162/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2579-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301003102 and revision id 13551\n -->\n"
